I te 21 o Awatea 1938, ka uru a Bogart ki te mārena tuatoru ki te kaiwhakaari o Mayo Methot, he wahine ngāwari, he hoahoa, ina whakaaro nui, he pōrearea, he pākaha hoki i te inu.
